      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/mesh-convergence-study",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence and discretization error quantification",
      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) computed on three systematically refined meshes (4.2M, 12.1M, 31.8M cells). GCI for NIH at the design point is 3.7%, satisfying the MRL 5 discretization error requirement."
    }
  ],
